{
  "id": 6583,
  "name": "Gluttonous Yumkasaur Mountain King",
  "desc": "A powerful Yumkasaur that has survived both the ravages of time and countless battles, surviving until the present day.<br>This \"Mountain King,\" who once joined forces with the great heroes against the Black Tide, holds a special place in the hearts of the Scions of the Canopy. Some tribe members believe that it has its current body shape because it has a unique physique, like the Qucusaurus \"Tyrant\"... Though in fact, this is simply because it's lived for so long, and eaten way, WAY too much.",
