              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>A Yumkasaurus that has experienced numerous impressive battles. It is not some abnormal mutant but has grown into its current shape due to its gluttony. It will collect Flamegranates during combat and spit them out as bombs. However, if you can use <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">Pyro to ignite the Flamegranates</span> before the Gluttonous Yumkasaur Mountain King can swallow them, who knows what might happen...</p>"
